-- Spain's Mapfre to finance Direct Line purchase with own cash
-- By Paul Day
-- Thu Sep 25, 2014 04:34AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, Sept 25 (Reuters) - Spanish insurer Mapfre <MPA.MC> said on Thursday it would finance the purchase of the Italian and German businesses of Direct Line <DLGD.L> with its own cash and did not rule out other European purchases.

